    "These modules introduce error cascades and cannot capture robot motion, yielding an incomplete physical representation (Fig. 3(c)).",
    "In contrast,TraceForge provides a lightweight pipeline that extends beyond in-lab data to in-the-wild videos, enabling the construction of large-scale training sets.",
